700132f-a.title: Bronx: 149th Street (East) - Bergen Avenue
700132f-a.text:
East 149th Street, north side, east from but not including Bergen Ave.
Also shown is the elevated structure of the Third Avenue elevated line
extension to the Lexington Avenue subway lline running on Westchester Ave.
May 1926.
Brown Brothers.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
